[
    {
        "source_sentence": "大乘中觀釋論卷第一",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "安慧菩薩造",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚卿光梵",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大師賜紫沙門臣惟淨等奉　詔譯1 觀緣品1觀緣品第一歸命一切智！",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有世俗、勝義二諦本無所行，若無所行，攝化有情事即當捨離。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩為開示故，造此《中論》。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然此不同一切外道所說緣生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說緣生法，為令覺悟多慢心者生極淨信。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於諸論中，此論宗重，謂緣生義，即無滅等句。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "最勝緣生，顯明開示，是故論初讚歎世尊。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如本頌言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不滅亦不生，　　不斷亦不常等。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "滅者，無常性故名滅。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "發起名生，斷生死故名斷，擇滅涅槃常時性故名常。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如有人言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a20_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若佛出世、若不出世，法性常住。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此緣生者，亦即是常。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者無差別義。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如所說離，此即是為緣生之法。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何所生邪？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂種種義，如其所說，從因所生、生已有果。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "來者向此名來。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無來義轉時，此即無去。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無去義轉時，即無過去世所行。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非今有滅，此即無滅。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此法如是，說餘生等亦然。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若取著言詮，即為戲論。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a27_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如其言詮，於如是性執有性者，彼皆息滅，此即名為滅諸戲論、離諸嬈惱性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136a29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "分別自性空已乃名寂靜。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今此如是無滅等十種句義，如前所說十種對治，此中皆止周盡，是論皆說此義，此如是義成，餘一切論中皆同此緣法。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今此義中，若此因、若彼緣，如薪生火，而彼所取如是應知。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常不斷義，如前句所說發起之義，此所說成。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若因中有故，設因壞時後還不離果起，無前後時性故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如澡沐已受食，此非緣生，若言無生，自語相違。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不和合對治，此即世俗緣生不和合故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若勝義諦所生，此中止遣。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世俗諦識中體性不和合勝義諦體性，此中止遣。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等是世俗？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等是勝義？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b11_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若勝上所說相續義性，以世俗諦伺察時此不和合，以彼現證非涅槃所得，此所作性不異勝義諦故，亦不止遣。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若智所成，即彼世俗諦不異勝義諦，如瓶等色等。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而此一類色受等法，決定境界智不許可，彼智無性故，譬如瓶等墮世俗有性，雖無所取，非世俗無。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中所說，世俗所取之義，是自非他，如理應知。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世俗者即是世俗所取故，如樹林等非極微許，而有所取道理可得。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若方分分別差別分別等性，而彼決定世俗有性，此非道理，以物體遍計有樹林等對礙，而識中有彼樹林等為所表故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b22_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然識中物性非無道理，由是樹於彼識而為所緣，如是能表識中得有所表，是故非物體樹於識中有。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此如是說故，餘說亦然。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b25_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於能表所表中，遍計無體亦無所成。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何法可成邪？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂如諸佛境界色等決定。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此何不成？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如彼諸佛境界，此亦然有，非如識中遍計生等此中止遣。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b28_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識中物體若有性者，此非道理。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136b29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若彼勝上如來之智，如所說義故名勝義，餘皆世俗，不實性故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此說最上，謂佛所說善文善義。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故頌言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我稽首禮佛，　　諸說中第一。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若文義二無著智性，唯佛大師而善宣說。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何所說邪？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂說無生性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今為證成無生性故，彼無滅等諸差別義亦如是證成，如是建立無生法故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有人言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所說生者，我知差別之性如是自生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為遮遣彼說，是故頌言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸法不自生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所言生者，本無今有之別名。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c10_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自者，我性義。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼如是說，互相損惱。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c11_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自語相違，不和合對治。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或如瓶等，即不見有自生之法，如前瓶等，自體無性故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸生法無性，生已復生，亦復無性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是眼等決定和合，若爾即有對治過失。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有如是因，即有如是果。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼果體有生，以因果二法無別異性故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若言自生，此應思擇。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復泥團離瓶，瓶離於因，此中色等當云何有？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若離泥團，果因二種無別異性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若泥團離瓶，而此果體即不和合。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "泥團若壞，瓶有所得，即非果時有因性故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此僧佉人言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如色等非果因二法有別異性，色等自體亦如離瓶先無有性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若彼決定實無所成，所說無異如瓶所作。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "杖輪水等非此所闕，彼等無別異性，因果二無性故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c24_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名無別異？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂不見因自體能作。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是果有所作，亦復不得，無異性故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c25_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無所作，何名因果？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "決定自體無別異性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若因無作，彼無作時果不和合。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有異人言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c27_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我知差別，諸法從他性生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為對遣彼說，是故頌言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c28_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「亦不從他生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0136c29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "他生者，別異義，如他性瓶等不生眼等。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由如是故，自緣既不生，他性亦然。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若止遣諸法自相，應知有過，此中或有彼不和合。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是所作，非勝義諦中他緣能生內六處等，以他性故，此如瓶等。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中他性瓶等如內六處緣勝義諦中生無性可得，世俗諦中亦然，生無性可得。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "相違義性無因生性及共生等。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有所得皆他義故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是所有，中論成就究竟義中離不和合對治等法。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復如是世俗諦中有所得者，決定如前對治相違。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世俗緣生有所得故，此亦非所得，如是有所成即和合無性成已見邊二不和合，如是即於諸所成中有共過失。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若別異所成，當知自有差別過失，此廣文不書，恐繁且止。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非《中論》所說，如前對治。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後對治亦爾，無此中所成和合道理。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有異人言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "取彼實有泥團，隨有杖等諸作用法共生瓶等。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此異意樂，故頌止言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「共生亦無性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼增上所作，言非二法共生，若爾有言說對治過失。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有異人言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如所意樂，諸法如是無因而生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為遣彼義，是故頌言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「亦不無因生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如他所說，無因生性有所得者，即時處等彼相離性決定有生可得。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼時處性能不相離，此若止遣對治過失。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中或有生性，諸論皆說是有漏義，如是有性各各繫屬。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸性有生，此中皆止。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有所作，即與阿含相違。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如佛所說，有四種緣能生諸法。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而此四緣，諸經論中皆如是說。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為四？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137a29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂因緣、所緣緣、次第緣、增上緣。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是四緣，無第五緣。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸異宗中有執我者、執極微者。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何所以邪？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中若有常因者，彼時處性即能相離，彼一切果乃有同生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "現見時處等不相離性，次第生法彼同作因，即不相離因性可得，此無過失。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故同作諸因此中非因，彼說如是生無有性，若有因故決定有果。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼同作諸因決定因性，此本有故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若同作因此相離者，即如前說對治相違，以本和合故，而彼諸因如是建立差別因無性，然彼處等有相離性可同生者，此之分位如士夫等。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由如是故非士夫等因本無和合性，士夫等句義亦如自體亦非定有。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "士夫等本性和合所有因性如種子等，以士夫等本來分位或離所作性，如種子等因有所得或無所得。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此復云何？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b15_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若本來分位離所作性或有所得，即是無常。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不離所作自相，亦即無因。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如前已說非諸士夫，如彼種子能生於果。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如是見，此非道理，彼遍計性故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故前說無第五緣，亦非斷滅。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世間所有諸執無因惡因諍論亂意之者，為攝化彼故，如其分位於世俗諦開示宣說諸因緣等，此即非勝義諦。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有問言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自果於緣中為有邪？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為無邪？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "物體第三分別無性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故頌答言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b23_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如諸法自性，　　不在於緣中。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如瓶衣，非即有故，亦非異故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是眼等自性，若自緣、若他緣、若共有，而彼諸緣非即非異。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若離自體即無有果，由自力能即有諸緣，此無異性應當思擇。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由如是故，因果二法無別異性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何所以邪？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若離是因，果不能成。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137b29_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼能作因，其義亦然。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若定有異性，而彼自果於諸緣中即無所生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故頌言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以無自性故，　　他性亦復無。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有此二，即互不相離。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若見有他性，如此彼二，非緣時中有果、非果時中有緣。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若他性隨生，即因果二法非俱時有，剎那性故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c06_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若生不生二所作性二俱無性，若不壞因未來有果，此智所安立乃說他性，然若取著他性非勝義諦有。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有人言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸經論中皆說他緣能生諸法，云何此說非他性生？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸緣中他性不生，豈可無自性諸法於緣中住？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若爾緣即是非緣。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若自性無所有者，果從他緣生即非道理。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故頌答言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「亦非緣生果。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然生法所作有果可成。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為總止餘義，是故頌言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「果不從緣有，　　有無果生止；",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若說生法時，　　無依無所生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "前說果不生無所成者，以能生果者自亦無性。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能生、所生及彼生法定有別異生法可得者，即彼所作說為能生，此中別異生法即無所成。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若果離於緣，即所生、生法云何得成？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "他所繫屬故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有人言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所作如是從緣所成，非物體自性成故，是故非眼等六處能成緣法。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有此意樂，故頌答言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「果不從緣生，　　此果緣中生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若彼決定別異生法為可有者，彼無生法中間所作若生，而彼眼等決定生法互相離性或如是生，亦何不成？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0137c29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是說者，彼無自性法，此中有過失。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此異宗說，是故有過。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若從緣生果，彼果性無依，緣亦無常，相離性中果云何成？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如有頌言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「果若別異解，　　無道理可依；",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若一法作成，　　果體不可立。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如本頌言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「非無緣有果，　　無緣果亦無；",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是世俗中，　　常性不可得。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋曰：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若或無緣，果即不成；",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有果故，彼諸法體即有所得，彼等諸法亦非先有性故，是義當知從緣所生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若離緣生，虛無有果，譬如芽等，何能和合？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若言從種生芽，即能生所生二和合故，亦非種子等緣一向能生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以餘法成即能有果，由如是故果非常有。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有人言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從緣有果，此即非常亦非無常，如是性中能生得成。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "釋者言：",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如汝所說，此有法故，即此所成。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是決定勝義諦中，非無緣有果、非無果有緣，俱不見故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眼等諸法此中亦然，於其緣性若止遣者，定知有過。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故當知，從緣有果。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a19_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸果體生，謂從因緣、次第緣、所緣緣、增上緣生故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以諸緣分別、果體差別如是得成，譬如已成熟果，而諸因體差別分別，是故能作所作此中分別。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此如是說決定有果，決定之言即印持義。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中有果其義顯明，世俗諦中果法增勝即有所得，然無分位可著。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若果性有著，即他宗義，謂於緣中非實有果。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若彼如是從緣生果，互相所攝有果隨轉，彼雖分位各別，然有果生，此說緣生。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故此等諸緣生已，亦各別故。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸未信許言，即是不樂說義。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138a29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若此果不生，即彼無有緣。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138b01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為緣？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138b01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂隨所意樂。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138b01_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故若無有緣能生於果，此無道理。",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138b02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若或無緣，又復何有緣性可生？",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138b03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大乘中觀釋論卷第一",
        "from": "T30n1567_001:0138b04_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]